WEBVTT

00:12.350 --> 00:15.280
[Young Chu Qiao]

00:18.090 --> 00:21.200
[Nine years ago] [Zhuge Xi's Villa]

00:24.510 --> 00:25.710
Search carefully!

00:26.030 --> 00:27.030
Find her quickly!

00:27.190 --> 00:27.960
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:28.800 --> 00:29.350
Search!

00:29.840 --> 00:30.850
Boss, are you okay?

00:30.850 --> 00:31.930
Get out of my way!

00:32.600 --> 00:33.880
Search carefully.

00:34.200 --> 00:36.600
Even if you have to turn
this place upside down,

00:36.600 --> 00:38.280
you must find that little slave.

00:38.280 --> 00:39.740
When I catch her this time,

00:40.470 --> 00:42.670
I'll skin her alive!

00:43.390 --> 00:44.070
Find her!

00:44.670 --> 00:45.330
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:46.000 --> 00:46.880
-Hurry.
-Let's go.

00:46.880 --> 00:47.350
Hurry.

01:09.280 --> 01:10.070
Who are you?

01:20.180 --> 01:22.860
[Yunniang, Qingshan Manor]

01:32.640 --> 01:33.700
You little wretch.

01:35.070 --> 01:36.470
You've got a lot of nerve.

01:37.430 --> 01:39.280
I'm going to flay you alive.

01:39.759 --> 01:40.560
Take her back!

01:41.680 --> 01:42.280
Stop.

01:42.759 --> 01:43.479
This little slave

01:43.479 --> 01:46.140
trespassed into
the Third Master's courtyard.

01:46.479 --> 01:49.430
She should be handled by us.

01:49.789 --> 01:51.430
Falling into their hands,

01:51.740 --> 01:52.800
you little wretch,

01:53.870 --> 01:55.430
you're going to suffer.

01:56.280 --> 01:56.840
Let's go.

02:04.430 --> 02:06.090
Aren't you going to punish me?

02:07.040 --> 02:08.970
This is not a place you should come.

02:09.240 --> 02:10.470
Don't come back next time.

02:10.470 --> 02:11.270
You can leave.

02:11.750 --> 02:12.800
I've heard of you.

02:13.080 --> 02:14.280
Linxi said

02:14.280 --> 02:16.940
the Third Master, Zhuge Xi,
likes women the most

02:17.190 --> 02:18.960
and likes killing them the most.

02:18.960 --> 02:20.470
Every day in this mansion,

02:20.470 --> 02:22.470
so many women
are sent to the third branch.

02:22.470 --> 02:24.430
No one comes out of that courtyard alive,

02:24.430 --> 02:25.290
except for you.

02:25.710 --> 02:27.970
You've survived in that hell for 3 years.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.590
You know quite a lot.

02:31.710 --> 02:33.680
Go away. Don't come near here again.

02:33.680 --> 02:35.960
Otherwise, even I can't save you.

02:37.840 --> 02:41.040
Do you think this courtyard
is the only terrifying thing?

02:41.120 --> 02:44.030
In the entire Zhuge family
and even the entire Zhenhuangcheng,

02:44.030 --> 02:45.560
isn't it like this everywhere?

02:45.560 --> 02:46.190
Wherever I am,

02:46.190 --> 02:49.050
aren't I just a slave
whose life is as cheap as grass?

02:50.560 --> 02:52.710
Please, teach me.

02:53.180 --> 02:54.300
I want to survive too.

02:54.300 --> 02:55.579
I know you're capable.

02:55.840 --> 02:57.770
You can survive by Zhuge Xi's side.

02:58.079 --> 02:59.910
I want to be as strong as you.

03:28.520 --> 03:29.190
Continue.

04:11.910 --> 04:12.630
Master.

04:14.750 --> 04:16.810
You've made fast progress recently.

04:16.920 --> 04:17.980
Thank you, Master.

04:18.160 --> 04:19.040
You are a slave,

04:19.680 --> 04:22.070
but do you know
there are 2 types of slaves?

04:23.720 --> 04:25.380
Please enlighten me, Master.

04:25.510 --> 04:26.160
One type

04:27.040 --> 04:28.270
is born a slave.

04:29.060 --> 04:30.260
That's their status.

04:30.870 --> 04:31.720
The other type

04:33.040 --> 04:34.510
is willing to be a slave.

04:35.320 --> 04:37.960
They even believe they are inferior.

04:42.720 --> 04:45.480
People can't choose their origins.

04:47.360 --> 04:49.830
But if they abandon their inner beliefs

04:50.460 --> 04:52.580
and completely accept their fate,

04:53.510 --> 04:55.240
then they are true slaves.

04:56.190 --> 04:58.320
As long as they don't give up fighting,

04:58.510 --> 04:59.950
whether under the sword

04:59.950 --> 05:01.310
or in this world,

05:02.240 --> 05:04.040
there is still a glimmer of hope.

05:14.920 --> 05:15.520
Take this.

05:17.340 --> 05:18.800
Why are you giving me this?

05:19.070 --> 05:21.190
Slaves can't accept these.

05:21.830 --> 05:23.120
I'm leaving here.

05:24.190 --> 05:25.650
I don't need this anymore.

05:26.000 --> 05:26.950
Hold on to it.

05:27.320 --> 05:28.720
Don't let Zhu Shun see it.

05:28.790 --> 05:29.800
Where are you going?

05:29.800 --> 05:31.600
Are you going back to your village?

05:31.600 --> 05:35.000
The village has long
been destroyed by war.

05:36.540 --> 05:38.060
I'm going to a new place.

05:38.800 --> 05:40.360
Is it the place you talked about,

05:40.360 --> 05:41.680
where there are no slaves,

05:41.680 --> 05:43.720
and people are not divided into classes?

05:43.720 --> 05:45.070
Can you take me with you?

05:49.040 --> 05:49.680
Remember,

05:50.560 --> 05:52.190
you must survive.

05:53.280 --> 05:54.430
Only by surviving

05:54.890 --> 05:56.770
can you go wherever you want to go.

06:14.640 --> 06:15.320
Wash!

06:16.160 --> 06:17.000
Wash faster!

06:18.000 --> 06:18.730
Steward Zhu!

06:19.000 --> 06:19.830
Something terrible has happened!

06:19.830 --> 06:20.480
What is it?

06:20.480 --> 06:21.270
Something terrible has happened!

06:21.270 --> 06:21.920
What is it?

06:22.750 --> 06:23.610
Have you heard?

06:23.680 --> 06:25.800
Yunniang failed to assassinate
the Third Master

06:25.800 --> 06:27.130
and was beaten to death.

06:27.560 --> 06:28.160
What?

06:28.390 --> 06:29.390
It's true.

06:29.630 --> 06:30.920
The Third Master was furious.

06:30.920 --> 06:33.060
He ordered his men to drag her corpse
to the hunting ground

06:33.060 --> 06:34.460
to feed the dogs.

06:37.800 --> 06:38.860
Whoever slacks off

06:39.159 --> 06:41.159
will be dragged out to feed the dogs!

08:25.140 --> 08:30.690
[REBIRTH]

08:31.030 --> 08:33.630
[Episode 27]

08:36.260 --> 08:38.190
[Chu's Mansion]

08:36.440 --> 08:37.720
This is Chu's Mansion?

08:38.150 --> 08:38.909
Of course.

08:39.720 --> 08:42.510
I'm no longer the noble young master
of the Zhuge family.

08:42.510 --> 08:46.170
I can only rely on you and marry into
the Chu family as your husband.

08:47.960 --> 08:48.820
What are these?

08:49.320 --> 08:51.060
These are colored knots
bought at the market.

08:51.060 --> 08:53.480
They are hung around the house
before moving in,

08:53.480 --> 08:54.480
to pray for peace.

08:54.740 --> 08:56.140
I'll hang them up for you.

09:11.840 --> 09:12.370
Go ahead.

09:23.080 --> 09:23.600
Done.

09:24.270 --> 09:24.840
How is it?

09:24.840 --> 09:25.670
Why do I feel like

09:25.670 --> 09:26.510
hanging them here isn't great?

09:26.510 --> 09:27.310
Young Master.

09:29.870 --> 09:30.530
Put me down.

09:31.240 --> 09:32.170
Y-Young Master,

09:32.200 --> 09:34.500
many Ximeng citizens
have gathered outside the palace.

09:34.500 --> 09:37.240
They tied up their daughters
and said they wanted to offer them to you.

09:37.240 --> 09:38.270
Offer them to me?

09:38.950 --> 09:46.700
-Long live King Ximeng!
-Long live King Ximeng!

09:46.720 --> 09:48.000
What are you doing?

09:48.320 --> 09:50.250
Why are their hands and feet bound?

09:50.790 --> 09:51.630
Your Majesty,

09:51.750 --> 09:53.910
to thank you for your great kindness,

09:54.030 --> 09:56.320
we are offering our unmarried daughters

09:56.480 --> 09:57.630
to you!

09:57.790 --> 09:59.320
I don't need female slaves.

09:59.480 --> 10:00.550
Take them home.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.010
Forgive us, Your Majesty!

10:02.080 --> 10:05.270
-Forgive us, Your Majesty!
-Forgive us, Your Majesty!

10:05.270 --> 10:07.000
I have already issued a decree.

10:07.240 --> 10:08.360
Your own daughters

10:08.470 --> 10:10.130
can't be given to me as slaves,

10:10.440 --> 10:12.670
nor can they be bought
and sold by you with a price tag.

10:12.670 --> 10:13.730
Do you understand?

10:14.270 --> 10:15.870
Ximeng is vast.

10:16.720 --> 10:18.270
There is room for all of us.

10:19.240 --> 10:22.300
Now that all tribes
can put aside their past grievances

10:22.320 --> 10:24.450
and gather in Ximengcheng to develop,

10:24.630 --> 10:26.790
at this rate, in a few years,

10:27.510 --> 10:28.630
herds of cattle and sheep

10:28.630 --> 10:30.890
and a life of plenty
will not be a fantasy.

10:30.960 --> 10:31.870
There is no need

10:31.870 --> 10:33.670
to live by exploiting slaves.

10:40.550 --> 10:41.350
Your Majesty.

10:42.200 --> 10:43.330
This is my daughter.

10:43.670 --> 10:44.800
She just came of age.

10:45.390 --> 10:47.050
She can serve your daily needs

10:47.870 --> 10:49.330
and do some heavy lifting.

10:50.390 --> 10:52.150
Please don't despise her.

11:12.030 --> 11:12.830
Your Majesty.

11:32.240 --> 11:32.840
Xing?

11:36.200 --> 11:36.830
Xing.

11:37.600 --> 11:38.660
What are you doing?

11:39.000 --> 11:40.060
Whose robe is this?

11:41.510 --> 11:44.440
It's what King Ximeng's
personal female slaves would wear.

11:44.440 --> 11:45.900
I've thought of a good idea

11:46.080 --> 11:47.360
to let those commoners

11:47.440 --> 11:49.900
stop sending their daughters
to the palace.

11:50.550 --> 11:51.390
Oh my god!

11:51.430 --> 11:53.230
King Ximeng is getting married!

11:53.270 --> 11:54.270
Getting married?

11:54.270 --> 11:57.270
Is he going to choose female slaves
for the palace again?

11:57.270 --> 11:58.000
No.

11:58.270 --> 12:00.840
It's a proper Queen Ximeng.

12:01.100 --> 12:02.570
The wedding will last for 3 days

12:02.570 --> 12:04.370
for all the commoners in the city

12:04.480 --> 12:05.960
to celebrate for him!

12:06.240 --> 12:06.920
Really?

12:06.940 --> 12:08.970
-That's great!
-That's great!

12:10.000 --> 12:11.440
Everyone, please line up.

12:11.440 --> 12:12.120
Don't push.

12:12.120 --> 12:12.720
-Thank you.
-Give me one.

12:12.720 --> 12:13.630
Don't push. Don't push.

12:13.630 --> 12:15.270
-There's enough for everyone.
-There's enough for everyone.

12:15.270 --> 12:16.550
Listen to me, everyone.

12:16.550 --> 12:17.840
There's enough for everyone.

12:17.840 --> 12:20.720
These are the wedding candies
of King Ximeng and the Queen.

12:20.720 --> 12:22.600
You can come back for more
when you finish.

12:22.600 --> 12:24.840
-Great!
-Great!

12:25.000 --> 12:26.440
They said King Ximeng is getting married.

12:26.440 --> 12:28.390
For 3 days, there'll be fairs in our city

12:28.390 --> 12:29.790
and free food for everyone.

12:29.790 --> 12:30.720
I also heard

12:30.870 --> 12:32.390
that after King Ximeng gets married,

12:32.390 --> 12:34.870
he won't need female slaves
to serve him in the palace anymore.

12:34.870 --> 12:37.030
I heard that Queen Ximeng

12:37.320 --> 12:39.050
was also a female slave before.

12:41.420 --> 12:44.220
-Go get another portion!
-Go get another portion!

12:45.370 --> 12:47.290
Freshly baked Queen's cakes!

12:47.600 --> 12:49.750
At King Ximeng and the Queen's
wedding tonight,

12:49.750 --> 12:51.880
these Queen's cakes are what they ate!

12:52.390 --> 12:53.510
Miss, Sir,

12:53.870 --> 12:55.270
freshly baked Queen's cakes.

12:55.270 --> 12:56.030
Crispy and fragrant.

12:56.030 --> 12:57.090
Here, have a taste.

13:00.000 --> 13:01.670
Since King Ximeng
has been fighting everywhere,

13:01.670 --> 13:03.150
he should keep it simple.

13:03.790 --> 13:05.320
I didn't expect him to make this.

13:05.320 --> 13:06.840
For the sake of the Queen, King Ximeng

13:06.840 --> 13:09.150
has even forbidden female slaves
from entering the palace.

13:09.150 --> 13:10.750
Making pastries is nothing.

13:11.550 --> 13:12.440
Miss, try it.

13:12.440 --> 13:13.390
It's delicious.

13:13.480 --> 13:15.280
I'll let him have a taste as well.

13:17.000 --> 13:17.910
How is it, Sir?

13:17.910 --> 13:18.840
Is it delicious?

13:20.550 --> 13:21.390
King Ximeng...

13:21.390 --> 13:21.750
Miss.

13:21.750 --> 13:23.360
-Has a real gift.
-Look at this.

13:23.360 --> 13:24.870
This is Luanfeng Tassel.

13:24.960 --> 13:26.510
King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng

13:26.510 --> 13:27.750
are wearing this pair.

13:27.750 --> 13:28.510
Really?

13:29.270 --> 13:30.150
I'll take it.

13:30.550 --> 13:31.150
Okay.

13:31.150 --> 13:33.610
Is this also
King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng's?

13:34.480 --> 13:35.240
Of course.

13:35.840 --> 13:36.440
Look,

13:36.670 --> 13:38.390
these two are a pair,

13:38.410 --> 13:40.110
threaded with the same string,

13:40.110 --> 13:42.080
symbolizing an endless marriage.

13:42.600 --> 13:44.360
King Ximeng and the Queen

13:44.360 --> 13:46.150
are a match blessed by heaven.

13:46.670 --> 13:47.270
Sir,

13:47.560 --> 13:49.360
-how about...
-I'll have a pair.

13:50.910 --> 13:53.030
Since King Ximeng
and Queen Ximeng have them,

13:53.030 --> 13:54.360
we should have them too.

13:54.370 --> 13:55.230
Just this pair.

13:55.280 --> 13:55.840
Okay.

13:55.840 --> 13:56.550
-Take them.
-Thank you.

13:56.550 --> 13:57.440
You're welcome.

13:57.440 --> 13:59.600
You must put these on each other

13:59.600 --> 14:00.530
for them to work.

14:30.670 --> 14:32.330
Why do you smell so good today?

14:33.160 --> 14:36.960
You didn't scent your robes
with incense before coming out, did you?

14:38.510 --> 14:39.320
How could I?

14:39.940 --> 14:41.340
I never use these things.

14:42.030 --> 14:44.630
It might be from the crowd.

14:47.910 --> 14:48.480
Let's go.

15:02.020 --> 15:03.930
♪ On the water ♪

15:04.110 --> 15:05.820
♪ Countless ♪

15:06.150 --> 15:07.830
♪ Ripples rise ♪

15:09.880 --> 15:12.060
♪ Let the wind shape ♪

15:12.130 --> 15:15.780
♪ Another me ♪

15:13.960 --> 15:15.020
-Zhuge Yue.
-Xing.

15:17.710 --> 15:19.710
♪ How can I escape ♪

15:19.740 --> 15:24.500
♪ All the reflections that hold you? ♪

15:25.120 --> 15:28.090
♪ Behind the illusions
of the moon in water ♪

15:25.480 --> 15:26.280
Young Master!

15:26.360 --> 15:28.150
Everything you asked me
to prepare is ready!

15:28.150 --> 15:29.360
Along with spices and wine!

15:29.010 --> 15:31.720
♪ I wait to sink deep ♪

15:31.740 --> 15:36.160
♪ May fortune smile on all below ♪

15:36.360 --> 15:39.950
♪ Just to hear when you'll come home ♪

15:36.870 --> 15:38.480
Lady Chu, look!

15:40.400 --> 15:42.400
♪ Braving schemes alone ♪

15:42.420 --> 15:44.140
♪ Treading through thorns ♪

15:44.170 --> 15:46.770
♪ Searching for your name ♪

15:46.840 --> 15:51.570
♪ Till storms rise again ♪

15:51.590 --> 15:55.480
♪ Not a single regret remains ♪

15:52.630 --> 15:54.630
Why did you prepare spices and wine?

15:55.500 --> 15:57.500
♪ Melt the ice ♪

15:57.240 --> 15:57.790
To drink.

15:57.530 --> 15:59.530
♪ That fate has wrought ♪

15:58.270 --> 15:59.120
To drink?

15:59.550 --> 16:04.760
♪ Let the night ♪

16:05.340 --> 16:10.660
♪ Forever glow ♪

16:31.150 --> 16:31.870
To drink?

16:32.840 --> 16:33.630
Zhuge Yue,

16:34.480 --> 16:36.240
you're a big liar.

16:51.090 --> 16:53.640
A handsome liar.

17:12.670 --> 17:15.540
Do you think our Young Master and Miss Chu

17:16.000 --> 17:19.270
have made it official or not?

17:21.030 --> 17:23.480
Judging from the sound, probably...

17:24.640 --> 17:25.750
mostly official.

17:27.400 --> 17:28.240
How about

17:29.510 --> 17:30.960
we give him another hour?

17:32.830 --> 17:33.920
In my opinion,

17:34.480 --> 17:35.920
it's definitely official.

17:35.920 --> 17:37.050
Let's all head back.

17:45.270 --> 17:47.750
King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng have decreed

17:48.510 --> 17:50.160
that from now on, regardless of gender,

17:50.160 --> 17:51.360
King Ximeng's Palace

17:51.510 --> 17:53.720
will no longer conscript
any slaves for labor.

17:53.720 --> 17:55.750
The commoners and tribes of Ximeng

17:56.200 --> 17:58.860
will no longer need
to send slaves to the palace.

18:08.640 --> 18:10.040
There is no need to kneel.

18:12.240 --> 18:14.920
I used to be just like you,

18:15.440 --> 18:16.550
a slave

18:17.030 --> 18:18.000
with no status,

18:18.550 --> 18:19.510
no name,

18:19.960 --> 18:21.000
no land, no house,

18:21.440 --> 18:22.790
and no right

18:22.790 --> 18:24.850
to decide whether I could live or die.

18:25.310 --> 18:26.400
In today's Ximeng,

18:26.510 --> 18:27.680
everyone is equal.

18:27.750 --> 18:28.920
I came to Ximeng

18:29.350 --> 18:32.400
and managed to break free
from the chains of power and status.

18:32.400 --> 18:33.830
You can all do the same.

18:34.550 --> 18:35.350
That gate

18:36.070 --> 18:39.240
used to be the place where you
sent away your family and children.

18:39.240 --> 18:39.960
Now,

18:40.750 --> 18:42.680
it is a passage connecting us.

18:43.200 --> 18:44.400
No matter who you are,

18:45.400 --> 18:46.660
if you have grievances

18:47.180 --> 18:48.380
or wishes,

18:48.880 --> 18:50.540
you can pass through that gate

18:51.230 --> 18:52.750
and find us in the palace.

18:58.680 --> 18:59.790
Go to the palace?

19:00.240 --> 19:01.350
Really?

19:02.240 --> 19:03.270
Can we really do that?

19:03.270 --> 19:04.160
Will it help?

19:10.970 --> 19:11.970
Please, stand up.

19:12.590 --> 19:13.720
Everyone, stand up.

19:24.200 --> 19:26.830
Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!

19:26.960 --> 19:30.270
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!

19:30.270 --> 19:33.000
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!

19:33.000 --> 19:35.750
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!
-Long live the King! Long live Ximeng!

19:35.750 --> 19:37.550
-Long live the King! Long live the Queen!
-Long live the King! Long live the Queen!

19:37.550 --> 19:39.110
-Long live Ximeng!
-Long live Ximeng!

19:39.110 --> 19:42.160
-Long live the Queen! Long live Ximeng!
-Long live the Queen! Long live Ximeng!

19:42.160 --> 19:44.560
-Long live the Queen!
-Long live the Queen!

19:51.160 --> 19:52.490
These are millet seeds.

19:52.680 --> 19:54.120
Register over there first,

19:54.120 --> 19:55.550
then go claim your land.

19:55.750 --> 19:56.310
Remember

19:56.350 --> 19:58.490
to choose a flat land
near the canal first.

19:58.490 --> 19:59.690
Thank you. Thank you.

19:59.880 --> 20:01.810
How many people are in your family?

20:01.880 --> 20:02.400
Three.

20:02.440 --> 20:03.890
No, 4.

20:04.000 --> 20:04.640
Four?

20:04.830 --> 20:06.200
Another one is about to be born.

20:06.200 --> 20:07.810
For 4 people, that's 8 mu of land.

20:07.810 --> 20:08.810
Can you manage it?

20:08.840 --> 20:10.470
The more, the better.

20:12.030 --> 20:12.750
How about this?

20:12.750 --> 20:13.960
I'll give you 2 more mu.

20:13.960 --> 20:14.510
Remember,

20:14.510 --> 20:16.350
if you can't farm it all,
hire someone first.

20:16.350 --> 20:18.070
If you hire someone,
you must pay them first.

20:18.070 --> 20:18.790
Got it?

20:19.790 --> 20:20.400
Take it.

20:22.750 --> 20:23.270
Well...

20:23.590 --> 20:24.980
Hey, come register.

20:25.480 --> 20:27.070
I'm hurrying back to farm the land.

20:27.070 --> 20:27.920
Register for what?

20:27.920 --> 20:30.110
What if you take the seeds
to make porridge instead?

20:30.110 --> 20:31.340
You'll get that 10 mu of land for nothing.

20:31.340 --> 20:32.600
Where would I find you?

20:34.570 --> 20:36.170
I wouldn't do that.

20:40.620 --> 20:41.550
Why are you here?

20:41.960 --> 20:43.790
I've come for land and seeds.

20:43.880 --> 20:45.140
What use is land to you?

20:45.160 --> 20:47.350
To provide for my newlywed wife.

20:48.030 --> 20:50.510
Ximeng's new decree
states that everyone is equal.

20:50.510 --> 20:52.160
Are you going to treat me differently?

20:52.160 --> 20:53.460
Since we're distributing land,

20:53.460 --> 20:55.220
I'll give him my 2 mu.

20:55.480 --> 20:57.280
Then I'll give you my 2 mu as well.

20:58.590 --> 20:59.440
Farm well.

21:03.920 --> 21:04.850
It really works.

21:05.510 --> 21:06.110
The water is here!

21:06.110 --> 21:07.240
-It's here.
-The water is here.

21:07.240 --> 21:08.570
-Let me see.
-Let me see.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.030
-There's water!
-There's water!

21:11.030 --> 21:12.750
This solves a huge problem for us!

21:12.750 --> 21:13.440
Yes.

21:14.510 --> 21:15.160
Yeah.

21:16.110 --> 21:16.790
Zhuge Yue!

21:23.880 --> 21:25.210
You know about farming?

21:25.350 --> 21:27.750
I used to think of farming books
as leisure reading.

21:27.750 --> 21:29.270
I didn't expect to use them today.

21:29.270 --> 21:31.750
You're truly a man of striking appearance
and extraordinary bearing.

21:31.750 --> 21:33.270
You are truly our savior.

21:44.920 --> 21:46.580
This awful journey is so hard.

21:46.750 --> 21:48.070
We don't even have a sip of water.

21:48.070 --> 21:50.720
Thankfully, we'll reach
Zhenhuangcheng soon.

21:50.720 --> 21:51.980
You can say that again.

21:52.440 --> 21:55.160
I dream of eating Tengxiang Restaurant's
Lotus Pouch Pork Tenderloin,

21:55.160 --> 21:57.790
Stir-Fried Lamb with Scallions,
Bamboo Shoots with Chicken and Goose,

21:57.790 --> 22:00.590
Lychee-Flavored Kidneys,
and Cured Donkey Meat.

22:00.880 --> 22:03.310
We can't get the other dishes,

22:03.720 --> 22:05.270
but wanting to eat donkey meat

22:05.270 --> 22:06.200
is easy.

22:09.270 --> 22:10.880
Whoever targets this donkey

22:11.510 --> 22:13.000
will get 200 strokes of the cane.

22:13.000 --> 22:14.200
-Yes, Sir!
-Yes, Sir!

22:18.400 --> 22:19.260
Your Highness,

22:19.580 --> 22:21.380
this is just an ordinary donkey.

22:21.750 --> 22:23.200
There is nothing special about it.

22:23.200 --> 22:25.200
Why do you care so much about it?

22:25.440 --> 22:26.840
This donkey is borrowed.

22:27.160 --> 22:29.450
Its owner is fierce
and not to be messed with.

22:29.450 --> 22:30.810
Neither of us can afford to offend her.

22:30.810 --> 22:33.410
Fierce? And can't afford to offend?

22:34.590 --> 22:35.350
Who is it?

22:49.560 --> 22:53.100
[Master of the Muhe Family, Great Yong]

22:59.520 --> 23:01.240
By His Majesty's decree,

23:01.590 --> 23:03.000
Your Highness, you deployed troops
without permission

23:03.000 --> 23:04.480
and are suspected of colluding
with the enemy and of treason.

23:04.480 --> 23:06.390
You're ordered to immediately
surrender the military tally,

23:06.390 --> 23:08.720
disarm, and be imprisoned pending trial.

23:08.720 --> 23:10.240
I asked Biantang for reinforcements

23:10.240 --> 23:12.880
and have written
to my father to state the urgency.

23:12.880 --> 23:14.000
As far as I know,

23:14.310 --> 23:15.910
my father has not recovered.

23:15.920 --> 23:17.050
May I ask, Lord Muhe,

23:17.160 --> 23:18.360
whose decree is this?

23:19.110 --> 23:19.760
That's right.

23:19.760 --> 23:22.310
I'm passing on
the Thirteenth Prince's decree.

23:22.310 --> 23:24.070
The Thirteenth Prince
is trumping up a charge,

23:24.070 --> 23:24.920
and he can easily find any excuse!

23:24.920 --> 23:25.400
Wait.

23:25.720 --> 23:26.580
Your Highness,

23:26.690 --> 23:28.350
I have a word of advice for you.

23:29.000 --> 23:29.930
What I represent

23:30.640 --> 23:31.900
is His Majesty's will.

23:32.470 --> 23:34.800
Even with thousands of troops behind you,

23:34.920 --> 23:36.920
if they dare to take
one more step forward,

23:36.920 --> 23:38.200
you will never

23:38.720 --> 23:40.590
clear yourself of treason.

23:46.070 --> 23:46.640
Fine.

23:47.750 --> 23:48.880
I'll go with you.

23:49.510 --> 23:50.370
Your Highness!

23:53.640 --> 23:54.480
You stay here.

23:55.110 --> 23:56.440
Don't do anything rash.

23:56.790 --> 23:57.650
Your Highness.

24:00.880 --> 24:01.550
Please.

24:16.970 --> 24:18.070
It's over just like that?

24:17.010 --> 24:21.910
[Zhao Yang,
the Thirteenth Prince of Great Yong]

24:20.110 --> 24:21.400
How boring.

24:22.160 --> 24:24.200
Father even told me to watch out for him,

24:24.200 --> 24:25.530
afraid he'd make a move.

24:27.240 --> 24:28.570
He worried for nothing.

24:41.830 --> 24:43.720
He handed over
the military tally just like that?

24:43.720 --> 24:44.920
Did he not resist?

24:46.070 --> 24:47.880
Your Majesty, he indeed did not.

24:48.400 --> 24:50.360
His Highness not only didn't resist

24:50.360 --> 24:52.690
but also stopped the soldiers behind him.

24:53.000 --> 24:54.030
After being imprisoned,

24:54.030 --> 24:56.480
he even took the initiative to hand over

24:56.480 --> 24:57.810
all 34 military tokens.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.000
Your Majesty,

25:00.110 --> 25:02.960
Lord Muhe said
since His Highness is a prince,

25:03.510 --> 25:06.400
whether to punish him
for colluding with the enemy

25:06.790 --> 25:09.160
still needs to be decided by you.

25:09.720 --> 25:12.240
He neither resisted my decree

25:12.720 --> 25:15.320
nor clamored for an audience
to argue his case.

25:15.550 --> 25:16.750
He is quite obedient.

25:17.680 --> 25:18.880
Lock him up for 3 days,

25:19.070 --> 25:20.070
then release him.

25:20.960 --> 25:21.550
Yes.

25:27.510 --> 25:29.310
Here is the edict of His Majesty.

25:34.880 --> 25:37.270
Seventh Prince Zhao Che
was arrogant due to his merits

25:37.270 --> 25:38.550
and privately mobilized reinforcements,

25:38.550 --> 25:39.830
which is an unforgivable crime.

25:39.830 --> 25:41.590
Considering his remorse,

25:41.750 --> 25:44.550
he's ordered to be stationed
outside Yanming Pass

25:44.750 --> 25:46.270
to redeem himself.

25:47.200 --> 25:48.600
I've received the edict.

25:55.790 --> 25:56.650
Your Highness.

25:58.590 --> 25:59.270
Rise.

26:17.550 --> 26:19.810
This gold coral hairpin is so beautiful.

26:23.240 --> 26:25.440
My Lady, you've done a great service
for His Majesty.

26:25.440 --> 26:27.240
Why are you still so worried?

26:27.750 --> 26:30.010
Although I helped His Majesty this time,

26:30.480 --> 26:32.680
my brother got mixed up with

26:32.680 --> 26:34.160
the Hongchuan Tribe and the Pale Tribe.

26:34.160 --> 26:36.490
His Majesty has always been deep-minded.

26:37.640 --> 26:39.970
Even if he endures it now
and says nothing,

26:40.270 --> 26:41.400
it's not guaranteed

26:41.740 --> 26:45.000
that he won't settle accounts
with the Helian family in the future.

26:45.000 --> 26:46.600
Please don't worry, My Lady.

26:46.960 --> 26:48.960
Look at the things His Majesty sent today.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.420
They are all what you like.

26:50.550 --> 26:52.440
It shows that His Majesty's not angry

26:52.440 --> 26:54.240
and cares about you very much.

26:54.550 --> 26:55.720
"Love me, love my dog."

26:55.720 --> 26:58.180
He definitely won't blame
the Helian Tribe.

26:58.830 --> 26:59.480
My Lady,

26:59.640 --> 27:01.970
Elder Helian Chuan requests an audience.

27:11.790 --> 27:13.510
I didn't even go looking for you,

27:13.510 --> 27:15.770
and you still have the nerve
to come to me?

27:15.830 --> 27:18.030
Today, Elder Tubu is hosting a banquet.

27:18.350 --> 27:20.750
The elders of the Hongchuan Tribe
and the Pale Tribe are there.

27:20.750 --> 27:22.210
For such a grand occasion,

27:22.630 --> 27:25.400
I want to take you out of the palace
to see the world,

27:25.400 --> 27:27.110
lest you be short-sighted

27:27.790 --> 27:28.880
and casually

27:28.990 --> 27:31.880
be brushed off by Yan Xun
with these cheap fabrics

27:32.030 --> 27:33.110
and jewelry.

27:55.550 --> 27:56.210
Delicious.

28:22.030 --> 28:23.960
After what happened the other day,

28:24.920 --> 28:27.350
the Hongchuan Tribe, the Pale Tribe,

28:27.880 --> 28:29.440
and our Helian Tribe

28:29.830 --> 28:31.360
have all been on the record.

28:32.110 --> 28:34.510
You can indulge in wine,
women, and gambling all you like.

28:34.510 --> 28:35.960
It won't cost you your head.

28:35.960 --> 28:37.400
Now you insist on taking yourself

28:37.400 --> 28:39.310
and the Helian Tribe down with you.

28:39.310 --> 28:40.310
Will you be satisfied then?

28:40.310 --> 28:42.880
If you hadn't helped
Yan Xun bring Huan Huan here,

28:42.880 --> 28:43.550
now,

28:44.480 --> 28:46.400
he would be a stray dog.

28:47.000 --> 28:49.270
You have done him a great service.

28:49.270 --> 28:50.350
At a time like this,

28:50.350 --> 28:52.160
you still dare to say such things?

28:52.160 --> 28:54.160
If you don't know
how to restrain yourself,

28:54.160 --> 28:55.290
when the time comes,

28:56.350 --> 28:57.810
I won't be able to save you.

29:01.290 --> 29:02.100
Ling, Ling.

29:02.920 --> 29:03.480
Ling.

29:04.020 --> 29:06.060
I know I've caused a disaster.

29:06.510 --> 29:08.590
So I want to ask you to do me a favor,

29:09.110 --> 29:10.960
have a casual meal with the elders,

29:10.960 --> 29:14.420
and put in a good word for me
in front of Yan Xun when you get back.

29:15.450 --> 29:16.310
My good sister,

29:16.680 --> 29:18.110
just help me out.

29:18.510 --> 29:20.350
I didn't want to mix with them either,

29:20.350 --> 29:21.750
but in the past half year,

29:21.830 --> 29:22.590
I've gradually

29:22.590 --> 29:24.680
received a lot of jade and fine horses
from them.

29:24.680 --> 29:26.550
It's too late for me to return them now.

29:26.550 --> 29:27.590
You also know,

29:27.790 --> 29:29.520
even Yan Xun is somewhat wary of

29:29.750 --> 29:31.680
the Hongchuan Tribe and the Pale Tribe,

29:31.680 --> 29:33.830
let alone me.

29:34.000 --> 29:36.200
I've given you so much. Isn't it enough?

29:36.400 --> 29:37.930
How dare you do such things?

29:38.030 --> 29:38.750
Ling,

29:39.350 --> 29:41.350
it's too late to say this now.

29:42.270 --> 29:42.960
Besides,

29:43.270 --> 29:45.350
for spring and summer grazing,

29:45.350 --> 29:47.350
our Helian Tribe all counts on them.

29:49.680 --> 29:51.830
Ling, my good sister.

30:15.000 --> 30:15.550
Come on.

30:16.000 --> 30:16.790
Elder Tubu.

30:17.510 --> 30:18.310
Elder Pale.

30:19.240 --> 30:20.070
Elder Yunmu.

30:29.350 --> 30:30.110
My Lady!

30:31.480 --> 30:32.400
My Lady.

30:33.590 --> 30:34.750
My Lady,

30:35.020 --> 30:36.590
why are you leaving so soon?

30:37.110 --> 30:39.590
Do you feel
we haven't taken good care of you?

30:39.960 --> 30:40.960
I thought I came here today

30:40.960 --> 30:43.420
to discuss serious matters
with the elders.

30:44.350 --> 30:45.310
But it seems

30:45.390 --> 30:47.560
the elders haven't had enough fun yet.

30:48.440 --> 30:50.030
Let's talk another day.

30:53.070 --> 30:54.130
What are you doing?

30:54.640 --> 30:56.640
Are you trying to imprison
the Consort of Great Yan?

30:56.640 --> 30:57.970
Do you have a death wish?

30:58.790 --> 30:59.790
We wouldn't dare.

31:00.740 --> 31:02.400
You misunderstand us, My Lady.

31:02.400 --> 31:04.110
If we weren't hosting you,

31:04.130 --> 31:06.590
how could we
be drinking and having fun here?

31:06.640 --> 31:09.030
My Lady, don't be so serious.

31:09.050 --> 31:09.760
That's right.

31:09.760 --> 31:10.930
Speaking of which,

31:10.950 --> 31:13.230
you and I have some history.

31:15.070 --> 31:18.200
Back then, her brother
wanted to marry her to me,

31:18.550 --> 31:20.610
in exchange for 500 of my fine horses.

31:22.200 --> 31:23.070
It's a pity

31:23.350 --> 31:26.150
I wasn't blessed enough to have you.

31:26.720 --> 31:29.680
Now that you've risen to power,

31:29.920 --> 31:32.880
you must be worth at least 2,000 horses.

31:34.130 --> 31:35.160
Elder Tubu, look at you.

31:35.160 --> 31:36.590
Two thousand horses?

31:37.240 --> 31:38.070
My Lady,

31:38.200 --> 31:40.160
please don't be angry.

31:40.310 --> 31:42.880
Elder Tubu was just joking with you.

31:43.440 --> 31:45.200
Yes, just joking.

32:09.070 --> 32:11.350
Elder Tubu, you're indeed wealthy.

32:11.640 --> 32:13.640
Not only can you trade horses for me,

32:14.620 --> 32:16.880
but even the wine for your casual banquet

32:16.880 --> 32:19.640
is the Western wine
rarely seen in the palace.

32:19.920 --> 32:21.880
But no matter how generous you are,

32:24.030 --> 32:26.070
you must be careful with your words.

32:26.640 --> 32:28.550
Insubordination is a capital offense.

32:28.550 --> 32:29.920
Once a person dies,

32:30.920 --> 32:32.920
horses won't bring them back.

32:36.590 --> 32:37.000
Well...

32:37.000 --> 32:37.880
Ling, Ling.

32:37.880 --> 32:40.280
Let's talk nicely
and not ruin the harmony.

32:41.750 --> 32:43.000
My Lady, please wait.

32:46.510 --> 32:48.070
I am clumsy with words

32:48.720 --> 32:50.450
and have offended you, My Lady.

32:51.600 --> 32:56.360
Recently, I've found a rare treasure,

32:56.380 --> 32:58.820
and I'd like to invite you
to appreciate it.

33:04.000 --> 33:04.680
This

33:05.240 --> 33:07.640
is the rare painting
I went to great lengths

33:07.750 --> 33:09.960
to find.

33:11.550 --> 33:13.030
The woman in this painting

33:13.660 --> 33:16.120
is the Queen
of the Ancient Chiling Kingdom.

33:16.350 --> 33:19.070
Just like you,

33:19.070 --> 33:22.790
she reduced taxes
and weakened the power of the nobles,

33:23.000 --> 33:24.720
allowing the local commoners

33:25.160 --> 33:27.240
to live a better and better life.

33:27.440 --> 33:28.400
What a pity.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.480
Quanrong invaded.

33:31.030 --> 33:33.400
They didn't just destroy
the Chiling Kingdom.

33:33.400 --> 33:34.600
The Quanrong leader,

33:34.880 --> 33:36.720
right in front of King Chiling,

33:36.880 --> 33:38.200
also raped the Queen

33:38.580 --> 33:41.860
and had a painter draw this rare painting,

33:42.590 --> 33:44.850
"The Painting of the Subjugated Queen."

33:47.410 --> 33:48.810
So that's what happened.

33:49.230 --> 33:50.950
Elder Tubu, on such an occasion,

33:50.950 --> 33:52.280
talking about such an obscene painting

33:52.280 --> 33:53.880
is probably inappropriate.

33:53.920 --> 33:57.550
My Lady, if you think
this is an obscene painting,

33:58.070 --> 34:00.070
you are too ignorant.

34:00.590 --> 34:01.960
For a man,

34:02.920 --> 34:05.750
insulting his opponent's woman
is a tactic.

34:06.110 --> 34:08.040
The Quanrong leader told the world

34:08.190 --> 34:08.710
that he

34:09.610 --> 34:11.699
trampled the dignity of King Chiling

34:12.630 --> 34:14.190
under his feet.

34:20.590 --> 34:21.760
Today,

34:23.030 --> 34:25.090
I will also trample Yan Xun's dignity

34:26.400 --> 34:28.190
under my feet.

34:28.760 --> 34:29.550
How dare you!

34:30.110 --> 34:31.440
Do you have a death wish?

34:35.880 --> 34:37.230
I dare!

34:40.880 --> 34:42.630
-What are you doing?
-Elder Tubu!

34:42.630 --> 34:43.550
Elder Tubu!

34:44.510 --> 34:45.630
Put me down!

34:45.920 --> 34:46.550
Ling!

34:46.840 --> 34:48.030
-Chuan!
-Helian, Helian.

34:48.030 --> 34:49.030
It's a good thing.

34:49.190 --> 34:49.550
You guys!

34:49.550 --> 34:50.480
Helian, Helian.

34:50.550 --> 34:51.590
Put me down!

34:51.590 --> 34:53.800
You've misunderstood
Elder Tubu's good intentions!

34:53.800 --> 34:55.130
Do you have a death wish?

34:55.840 --> 34:56.969
Today, you only said

34:57.110 --> 34:59.150
you wanted my sister to be a persuader.

34:59.150 --> 35:01.190
Nobody mentioned anything about this.

35:01.190 --> 35:02.190
Helian!

35:02.210 --> 35:03.230
Think about it.

35:03.360 --> 35:05.620
Ever since your sister became a Consort,

35:05.750 --> 35:07.350
who still respects you?

35:07.670 --> 35:09.670
If we don't help you
take her down a notch,

35:09.670 --> 35:12.360
there will be no place
for you in the Helian Tribe.

35:12.360 --> 35:14.360
But she is still a Consort after all.

35:14.360 --> 35:16.150
If Yan Xun hears about this...

35:16.150 --> 35:17.230
You are foolish.

35:17.670 --> 35:18.360
For this kind of thing...

35:18.360 --> 35:19.960
-Helian Chuan!
-If neither of us says anything,

35:19.960 --> 35:21.030
how could a weak woman like her

35:21.030 --> 35:22.480
possibly spread this around?

35:22.480 --> 35:23.030
Scream!

35:23.030 --> 35:25.960
Besides, Elder Tubu
has always known his limits.

35:26.280 --> 35:27.920
In matters of romance,

35:28.110 --> 35:29.840
he definitely won't force her.

35:30.760 --> 35:33.480
To put it plainly,
it's just mutual consent.

35:33.630 --> 35:35.230
Not only has the Helian Tribe
been bolstered

35:35.230 --> 35:36.960
by the title of Consort Helian,

35:37.280 --> 35:39.150
but they can also connect with Tubu.

35:39.150 --> 35:41.150
Isn't this the best of both worlds?

35:43.900 --> 35:44.920
You guys come here

35:44.920 --> 35:46.590
and serve Master Helian well.

35:46.590 --> 35:47.440
Come, come.

35:48.000 --> 35:48.630
Elder.

35:49.960 --> 35:51.440
Let's go, come on.

35:51.440 --> 35:52.400
Keep having fun.

35:57.340 --> 35:57.960
Let me go.

35:57.960 --> 35:58.880
You wretch!

36:00.400 --> 36:02.600
Do you really think you're the Consort?

36:10.710 --> 36:11.510
No!

36:26.630 --> 36:27.320
Tubu,

36:27.540 --> 36:28.870
do you have a death wish?

36:29.390 --> 36:31.250
How dare you assault the Consort!

36:32.430 --> 36:33.230
Consort?

36:33.720 --> 36:35.250
What kind of Consort is she?

36:35.550 --> 36:37.150
Yan Xun offered a high price,

36:37.190 --> 36:39.120
so the Helian family broke the deal

36:39.360 --> 36:40.800
and sold her to him.

36:41.080 --> 36:42.550
In the years she's been a Consort,

36:42.550 --> 36:44.440
how many times
has Yan Xun even looked at her?

36:44.440 --> 36:46.550
If I hadn't graced her
with my favor today,

36:46.550 --> 36:48.480
she wouldn't even have been worthy

36:48.920 --> 36:50.230
to serve me!

37:08.590 --> 37:09.510
Cheng Yuan.

37:17.000 --> 37:19.000
I was wondering why Consort Helian

37:19.000 --> 37:20.920
is different from the rumors.

37:21.190 --> 37:24.590
It turns out I'm a step too late.

37:24.590 --> 37:27.510
General Cheng,
you're quite lucky with women.

37:28.880 --> 37:30.760
Why don't you

37:32.990 --> 37:34.840
share it with us?

37:39.590 --> 37:40.880
Do you dare touch me?

37:41.030 --> 37:44.440
You really are His Majesty's lapdog.

37:44.760 --> 37:47.240
Not only are you like brothers,

37:47.440 --> 37:49.670
but you can even share the same woman.

37:56.070 --> 37:57.030
Elder Tubu!

37:57.280 --> 37:58.000
Elder Tubu!

37:58.230 --> 37:58.960
Elder Tubu!

38:11.150 --> 38:11.670
Go!

38:23.190 --> 38:23.800
Helian.

38:31.320 --> 38:32.190
Cheng Yuan.

38:34.350 --> 38:34.950
I...

38:36.960 --> 38:37.840
I killed him.

38:38.360 --> 38:39.070
Cheng Yuan.

38:41.740 --> 38:42.540
It's okay now.

39:10.030 --> 39:10.840
Zhuge Yue.

39:11.630 --> 39:12.550
Up until now,

39:12.710 --> 39:14.440
how many women have you liked?

39:14.460 --> 39:16.170
Did you specifically call me out

39:16.170 --> 39:17.740
just to tell me this?

39:18.110 --> 39:20.510
You are sinking into an abyss of pain,

39:20.800 --> 39:23.000
but I can let you see

39:23.000 --> 39:25.000
the person you miss.

39:25.000 --> 39:27.360
In the future, you will not only
be the King of Great Yong

39:27.360 --> 39:29.230
but also the King of the world!

39:29.230 --> 39:29.800
Traitor!

39:29.880 --> 39:31.630
How dare you impersonate King Ximeng!
